<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利向阿克拉解释了他的计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，阿克拉和格瑞布拉德开始准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两只狼在水牛群里跑进跑出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把牛群分成两组。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>母水牛和小水牛在一组，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们一边怒视，一边用蹄子刨地，准备攻击狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公水牛站在另一组。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们更大，看起来更吓人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但毛克利知道他们不如母水牛危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公水牛没有小水牛需要保护。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利跳到拉玛的背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉，把你的牛群往左边赶，赶向这条大峡谷的顶峰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德，你把母水牛们赶到峡谷的另一端，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让它们呆在那里，直到我们下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉嚎叫着，他的队伍出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德开始把母水牛们引向相反的方向。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，一些村里的孩子看着这样的场面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们带着牛飞快往家跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水牛疯了。它们在逃跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的计划很简单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他计划把谢尔坎困在两群水牛中间的峡谷里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎刚刚吃了一顿大餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很难战斗或爬上峡谷的两侧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利把困惑的公水牛们聚集在峡谷的顶峰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们站在一个通向峡谷的长满草的斜坡上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”毛克利看着峡谷侧壁想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侧壁几乎是垂直的，上面长满了茂密的藤蔓，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那会使老虎更难爬出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利举起一只手示意阿克拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他把手放在嘴里，朝峡谷下大喊：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎！”回声从一块石头传到另一块石头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一声咆哮回答道：“谁在叫我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我，毛克利！”他转向阿克拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把牛群赶下来！下去，拉玛，下去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他命令水牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公水牛群站在斜坡边上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉大叫了一声，它们向前跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们一个接一个地跑下去，就像被洪水冲下去的巨石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在峡谷里，拉玛很快就闻到了谢尔坎的气味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，水牛们知道他们的任务是什么了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是袭击老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚开始，谢尔坎听到了雷鸣般的蹄声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来，左看右看，试图找到一条路逃出峡谷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但峡谷壁笔直，满是弯曲的藤蔓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，吃了一顿大餐后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正觉得犯困，身子发沉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛群跑过水沟，溅起水花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>动物们大声吼叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利听到峡谷另一端母水牛们的回应。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎转身看向那些母水牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，老虎突然转向公水牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎本能地知道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面对他们要比面对任何一头保护小水牛的妈妈都容易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，拉玛被绊了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他身后的野兽们猛烈地撞向靠近的母水牛们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，两个水牛群都冲过峡谷，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>边跑边愤怒地喷着鼻息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利从拉玛的背上跳下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快，阿克拉！在它们开始打架之前，把它们分开。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉和格瑞布拉德绕着水牛跑，试图把它们分开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，水牛群转向了毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们准备再次冲进峡谷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但毛克利举起手来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎已经死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，饥饿的鸟儿就会来找他的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>